title: Moonlight, Miracles, and Marquise Brown | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We tell you the players to go big or go home on heading into Week 11 (1:30), show love for the Redskins against the Jets, argue about Marquise Brown, and highlight handcuffs to snag prior to the fantasy playoffs (19:30) before we build our daily fantasy lineup for the weekend (34:20).
Hosts: Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck
